{"type": "article", "id": 13837, "title": "让你“下线”的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-21T08:09:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185131xDCJ1gQboh2HmNe0.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款能够让你“下线”的椅子，首先，高高的椅背三面环绕，上方还有一个小小的遮棚，筑构了一个足够私密的空间。其次，椅子的右手边设计了一个小布袋，当手机放进去，信号和 Wifi 会被袋子特殊的材料设计屏蔽掉，留给你一个没有信息干扰的小世界，因此叫做“下线椅子”。<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/28518075/Offline-chair-blocks-off-mobile-and-WI-FI-signals-Star\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141521MtIePAwFVUuJD6o7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61858191\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614152279CdEjMBRbq1QsPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141522BypCUkeOVoTSmxvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141523BWJIXQAVwtdPmMu9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141523742hxMuBGadSeCYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57457213\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141524rVtHRL6DSczli7jO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141524pln4BhGg5iPE23x8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141525cSZ04nyBxazEqLOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}